#

Saffron Infused Lemon Garlic Shrimp Bisque with Chive Oil

$18.5
320 kcal
Difficulty: 60%

Allergens:

ShellfishDairy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeLow-CarbHigh-Protein

Tags:

SeafoodSoupGourmetLuxury

Description

A luxurious bisque with a vibrant saffron flavor, enhanced by zesty lemon and aromatic garlic, finished with a drizzle of fresh chive oil.

Ingredients

  • Large shrimp, peeled and deveined: 1 lb
  • Olive oil: 2 tbsp
  • Garlic, minced: 4 cloves
  • Shallots, chopped: 2
  • Saffron threads: 1/4 tsp
  • Chicken broth: 4 cups
  • Heavy cream: 1 cup
  • Lemon juice: 2 tbsp
  • Chives, finely chopped: 1/4 cup
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black pepper: to taste
